Carefully cradling her newborn to her chest, these heartwarming new photographs show a gorilla's sweet maternal side.

Mary, who lives at the Busch Gardens wildlife park in Tampa, Florida, gave birth to a little girl on February 6 at 8:30pm.

Images of the 27-year-old new mother capture her feeding her one-week-old daughter and admiringly looking at her in her arms.

